Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:54.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}你看  我們相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}各自的夢想
