Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.34,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:45.92,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(100,100)}閃著耀眼光芒的太陽
